00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,480
[Characters, behaviors, locations, departments,
careers, and situations in this series

2
00:00:02,520 --> 00:00:05,000
are made for entertainment purposes only,

3
00:00:05,040 --> 00:00:07,520
